  "text": "Xiao et al. [CITATION_1] proposed a technique for layer extraction by first obtaining regions of seed correspondence and then growing them to arbitrary shapes using the graph cuts approach integrated with level sets based formulation. The reader is suggested to refer to [CITATION_2] work for a more detailed survey of layer extraction work.",
